<sect2 id='gimp-layer-mask-menu' lang="en;cs;de;fr;zh_CN">
  <title>
    <phrase lang="en">Mask</phrase>
    <phrase lang="cs">Maska</phrase>
    <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Maske</quote></phrase>
    <phrase lang="fr">Masque</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">蒙板</phrase>
  </title>

  <figure>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en'>The Mask submenu of the Layers menu</phrase>
      <phrase lang='cs'>Podnabídka Maska nabídky Vrstva okna obrázku</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Das Untermenü <quote>Maske</quote></phrase>
      <phrase lang='fr'>Le sous-menu Masque du menu Calques</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">图层菜单的蒙板子菜单</phrase>
    </title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject lang="en;cs;de">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/menus-layer-mask.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="fr">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/fr/menus-layer-mask.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
      <imageobject lang="zh_CN">
        <imagedata fileref='../images/menus/zh_CN/menus-layer-mask.png'
          format="PNG" />
      </imageobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>

  <para lang='en'>
    The Mask submenu of the Layers menu contains operations that involve a
    layer mask: creating one, applying one, deleting one, or converting one
    into a selection. See the
    <link linkend='gimp-layer-mask'>Layer Masks</link>
    section for more information on layer masks and how to use them.
  </para>
  <para lang='cs'>
    Podnabídka <guisubmenu>Maska</guisubmenu> nabídky
    <guimenu>Vrstva</guimenu>
    obsahuje operace ovlivňující masku vrstvy. The Mask submenu of the Layers
    menu contains operations that involve a layer mask: creating one, applying
    one, deleting one, or converting one into a selection. See the
    <link linkend='gimp-layer-mask'>Layer Masks</link>
    section for more information on layer masks and how to use them.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    In diesem Untermenü finden Sie verschiedene Kommandos, um mit Masken zu
    arbeiten. Informationen wie Masken in <application>GIMP</application>
    eingesetzt werden können finden Sie im <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask"/>.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    Le sous-menu Masque du menu Calques contient des commandes concernant les
    masques de calque: Ajouter, Appliquer, Effacer ou Convertir en sélection
    un masque de calque. Voir <link linkend='gimp-layer-mask'>Layer 
    Masks</link> pour plus d'information sur les masques de calques et la 
    façon de les utiliser.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    图层菜单的蒙板子菜单包括与图层蒙板相关的操作：新建，应用，删除和转变为选区。关于图层蒙板以及如何使用它的更多信息请看
    <link linkend='gimp-layer-mask'>图层蒙板</link>
    章节。
  </para>

  <sect3 lang="en;de;fr">
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate submenü</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Untermenüs</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Activer le Dialogue</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>
          You can accede to it via 
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>L</accel>ayer</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>M</accel>ask</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Untermenü kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>M</accel>aske</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang='fr'>
          Vous le trouverez dans
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>C</accel>alque</guimenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>M</accel>asque</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>

  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang='en;fr;zh_CN'>Mask Menuitems</phrase>
      <phrase lang='de'>Der Inhalt des Untermenüs</phrase>
    </title>
    
    <para lang="de">
      Im Untermenü <guilabel>Maske</guilabel> stehen Ihnen folgende
      Kommandos zur Verfügung:
    </para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-add" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-apply" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-delete" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-selection-replace" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem lang="en;de;zh_CN">
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-selection-add" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem lang="en;de;zh_CN">
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-selection-subtract" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem lang="en;de;zh_CN">
        <para>
          <xref linkend="gimp-layer-mask-selection-intersect" />
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>